Class HDBOfficer

java.lang.Object
BTO_System.HDBOfficer
public class HDBOfficer extends Object
Represents a Housing Development Board (HDB) Officer who can register for projects and perform administrative tasks such as booking flats and generating receipts. An HDB Officer extends Applicant, meaning they can also apply for BTO projects personally.
